print("Welcome to the split bill calculator.")##Printing an introduction line
bill = int(input("How much is the bill?: "))##Asking user to fill a number for "bill" variable.
people = int(input("How many people are present?: "))##Asking user to fill a number for the "people" variable.
finalprice = bill/people##finalprice is a variable that divides the bill by amount of people.
print("You each owe",finalprice)##printed statement along with the calculation done.
